OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome evening
OL,6,Fsunshine away from the far north, then
OL,7,Fthe cloud there will extend south
OL,8,Facross much of the region tonight,
OL,9,Fwith the odd light shower.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FA cloudy start for most, the
OL,12,Fodd light shower, then all areas will
OL,13,Fbrighten up with some good sunny
OL,14,Fspells in the afternoon.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunny
OL,17,Fspells on Sunday, then cloudier in
OL,18,Fevening, patchy rain. Cloudy Monday,
OL,19,Fpatchy rain, then drier, brighter
OL,20,Flater. Tuesday dry, some sunny
OL,21,Fintervals, turning warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
